Name: Restart Selectable A-Rank Weapon Chest
Desc: Use this item in your Storage to select and obtain one of the following A-Rank W-Engines: Precious Fossilized Core, Rainforest Gourmet, Starlight Engine, Slice of Time, Original Transmorpher.
Desc2: A custom W-Engine giftbox for those looking to restart their business. If you want to give your new career a boost, this is more than worth the cost.
